@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@memberId = 1
@sessionId = 1

### 예약 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
X-MEMBER-ID: {{memberId}}
Idempotency-Key: reservation-key-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": {{sessionId}},
  "participantCount": 2
}

### 같은 Idempotency-Key / 같은 요청 재시도
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
X-MEMBER-ID: {{memberId}}
Idempotency-Key: reservation-key-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": {{sessionId}},
  "participantCount": 2
}

### 같은 Idempotency-Key / 다른 요청 - 실패 예상
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/reservations
X-MEMBER-ID: {{memberId}}
Idempotency-Key: reservation-key-123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionId": {{sessionId}},
  "participantCount": 3
}
